e=EN>Adoryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 321<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/02 2:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> They seem kind of common in the King room from my experiences... not sure about other areas. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usolosi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Solosi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/10/02 2:31 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> I've been thru the king room only once, normal ice gobs up and lower down there were maybe 1 or 2 patriarchs, a sage, and some elite guys.  I'm 53 and I can clear any other room with Jyll's...can I do the same to these guys?  Can I clear king room solo? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udanenel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Danenel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br>  Posts: 718<br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/11/02 5:53 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Heart of Frost</span><hr size=1> I'd not recommend jumping into King with Jylls... if you had the 2 jylls spells to alternate it might work... but really be safe. I cleared King alot solo around 54ish ... it's really easy to open up with Root, then snare (for when root breaks), then Draught of fire till dead. Works simple, is fairly safe.<br>
<br>
That said I saw the most hearts around Scryer room from gob wizzys.<br>
